{"tid":2081022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國白宫已修改《香港自治法案》","createTime":"2020-06-27T01:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T04:26:18.000Z","uid":134071,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5ecdb2943c7bf2662b8682861ec7cbd512bf3d81","tid":2081022,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T01:33:43.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》報道，由於《香港自治法案》設立強制制裁，特朗普政府官員曾有反對，指法案窒礙政府與中國進行外交的能力，亦在外交上給予國會太大權力。本月初加入成為法案共同提案人的共和黨參議員克拉默（Kevin Cramer）表示，他上周三提出反對，令參議院無法一致通過法案而押後表決，是應白宮要求，讓政府可跟議員談判，以修改法案一些技術和政策問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《華爾街日報》指出經磋商後，法案修改了一些細則，</strong>令白宮執行有關制裁時有一定彈性，消除了政府一些保留，<strong>但仍然未解決的問題是，法案讓國會參、眾兩院分別有逾三分二絕大多數票通過聯合決議下，可駁回總統豁免或中止制裁的決定。</strong><br />\n<br />\n克拉默則表示，有關財政部制裁的多個技術性修改完善了法案，令法案更有可能得到白宮肯首。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200627/YXRDVBIA5XNRL5F26VJGO5X5N4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2FYXRDVBIA5XNRL5F26VJGO5X5N4%2F&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=2b7b9ed9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2FYXRDVBIA5XNRL5F26VJGO5X5N4%2F&h=39680b6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200627/YXRDVBIA5XNRL5F26VJGO5X5N4/</a>"},{"pid":"ad8ea0c43074f8993dca9d56af29962e3ea4e19c","tid":2081022,"uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T01:34:49.000Z","msg":"希望House快d過<br />\n但睇會期，可能等到7月第二星期先會過。。。。"},{"pid":"425319ae88827518c1205dcd393414b2675431c3","tid":2081022,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ad8ea0c43074f8993dca9d56af29962e3ea4e19c","tid":2081022,"uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T01:34:49.000Z","msg":"希望House快d過<br />\n但睇會期，可能等到7月第二星期先會過。。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T01:37:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.house.gov/legislative-activity/2020-06-09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/l